# Validation & Definition of Done

Do not say "done" without evidence. **Full procedure: `e2e-verification.mdc`** (lint + build + E2E flows).

## Quick reference

```bash
bun run lint && bun run build
```

Then run smoke + feature E2E from `e2e-verification.mdc` Step 2–3.

